    Class Description
    ArrayTools
    Useful array tools.
    DelegatingMap<K,V>
    A DelegatingMap is a HashMap that delegates to another map for keys that do not have a value.
    LazyMap<K,V>
    A LazyMap is a Map that generates default values for keys that do not yet have a value.
